flowchart TD
    Sources[Data Sources\nWeb crawl, APIs, Uploads] --> Fetch[Fetch raw content]
    Fetch --> Parse[Parse and extract text]
    Parse --> Normalize[Normalize and tokenize]
    Normalize --> Stem[Stem and remove stop words]
    Stem --> Enrich[Enrich with metadata\nentities, embeddings]
    Enrich --> Dedupe{Duplicate\ncontent?}
    Dedupe -->|Yes| Discard[Discard duplicate]
    Dedupe -->|No| Score[Compute quality score]
    Score --> Index[Write to inverted index\nposting lists]
    Index --> Commit[Commit segment]
    Commit --> Shard[Distribute to shards]
    Shard --> Searchable[Document searchable]
